{"tid":620263,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩食飯老豆老母係度講譚詠麟有首歌叫...","createTime":"2018-04-07T11:56:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-07T15:04:48.000Z","uid":98507,"like":8,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"7ff5a52843de03196661db95778b1ce2cddde7d5","tid":620263,"uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T11:56:06.000Z","msg":"岩岩食飯老豆老母係度講譚詠麟有首歌叫咩定對錯、誰憑情來、情來誰<br />\n係度鳩up左成分鐘都講唔出<br />\n跟住頂唔順用好有自信嘅聲線講<br />\n淫憑誰來對定錯對下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知老豆走去YouTube search嗰時<br />\n佢問我 邊個淫呀？<br />\n我話任性個任呀<br />\nsearch完老豆再話 情憑誰來定錯對呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你都唔識嘅<br />\n<br />\n我心諗 我真係以為叫任憑誰來定錯對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 走去Google先知比咸歌王洗左腦<br />\n而家隔離檯有班後生仔係度對住我陰陰笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 柒到爆"},{"pid":"84a4db7754f5cad72ad1cb491c257230e81da15f","tid":620263,"uid":53673,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T12:11:25.000Z","msg":"條賓周係你個咀"},{"pid":"210d18570e3478cdffa1140c6a337539f0d12b6e","tid":620263,"uid":41908,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T12:12:27.000Z","msg":"寂寞路上爛閪窿～"},{"pid":"86ae9b674ce44cd1400f539943d12871733daf5d","tid":620263,"uid":35547,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T12:15:18.000Z","msg":"碌鳩裡有你的閪水"},{"pid":"d7f6b8bd0451eb5105a9719ab05966366ff11d06","tid":620263,"uid":17669,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T12:17:11.000Z","msg":"如能從頭遇見你"},{"pid":"0e822bfc8dc0ae596acb806a6f973fbfe66cd433","tid":620263,"uid":100230,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T12:17:14.000Z","msg":"轆尻裡也有你的閪水"},{"pid":"1fe1dbb7f06574f898ca047af5964deb7a8db660","tid":620263,"uid":17669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7f6b8bd0451eb5105a9719ab05966366ff11d06","tid":620263,"uid":17669,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"ci